      Frees memory allocated for a previously loaded or created image.
    </para>
  </refsect1>

  <refsect1>
    <title>Syntax</title>
    <synopsis><command>imagefree</command> iimagenum</synopsis>
  </refsect1>

  <refsect1>
    <title>Initialization</title>
    <para>
      <emphasis>iimagenum</emphasis> -- reference of the image to free.
